  "title": "ASSISTANT ENGINEER",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Expertise in identifying, formulating and producing effective solutions to emerging problems.</li>\n  <li>Manages the site coordination and project successful implementations.</li>\n  <li>Holds a diploma in Mechanical Engineering.</li>\n  <li>More than 12 years of experience.</li>\n  <li>Works for 6 days, sometimes 7 days in a week.</li>\n  <li>Evaluate final projects' overall costing and profitability.</li>\n  <li>Has knowledge in Warehouse and logistics.</li>\n  <li>Prepares Single line drawings and outline designs.</li>\n  <li>Manages to prepare claims and corresponding invoices.</li>\n  <li>Supports the management in successful business with confidentiality.</li>\n  <li>Holds Class 3 licence.</li>\n  <li>Has knowledge of MS office / Autocad drawings.</li>\n  <li>Has Risk Management bizSAFE level 2 Course.</li>\n</ul>",
